## Overview

This lab focuses on system hardening using **AWS Systems Manager Patch Manager**.  
I configured automated patching for Linux and Windows EC2 instances using default and custom patch baselines, and verified patch compliance.

---

## Architecture / Setup

- 3 Linux EC2 instances  
- 3 Windows EC2 instances  
- All instances managed via AWS Systems Manager (IAM role attached)

